== Path to Adoption ==

Our strategy focuses on:

* __Validation through Practice__: Pilot tournaments and demonstrations
* __Stakeholder Engagement__: Early consultation with officials from all major organizations
* __Gradual Implementation__: Allowing organizations to adopt at their own pace
* __Cultural Sensitivity__: Addressing specific concerns of each Go tradition
* __Technical Support__: Ensuring software and training materials are ready

